         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Goodbye. The 2nd year, Tybi 30. Patron to --ippos, greeting. Ptolemaios the merchant's son has written to Ö his father of the way in which we instructed you about the 50 drachmas o as to make another loan (?) until our boat starts. Give him therefore my letter lest you lose the chance. I have written for you a copy of his letter to me and of what he writes to his father. He brings you some Ö lotus-fruit. Goodbye. The 2nd year, Tybi 30.</ab>
         </div>
